strings: <voice_0x01001616><se_low>the force: No more bans, no more feeling!
<voice_0x01001617><se_def>China: What are you doing here Marcelo?
<voice_0x01001619><se_def>awesome!: I don't want to die in a pit, but it's never too late to pay your debts.
<voice_0x0100161A><se_def>awesome!: I don't care if they live or die.
<voice_0x01001620><se_def>awesome!: But I am still very grateful to Angel.
<voice_0x01001621><se_def>awesome!: Then text him "we are the same".
